text: Pentti Salo (born 14 October 1941) is a Finnish wrestler. He competed in the men's Greco-Roman 78 kg at the 1968 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1941 births Category:Living people Category:Finnish male sport wrestlers Category:Olympic wrestlers of Finland Category:Wrestlers at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:People from Lapua
